-- Bucharest Plans Sewage, Lake Water Drainage Contracts
-- B y   A n d r a   T i m u
-- 2013-04-05T13:25:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-05/bucharest-plans-sewage-lake-water-drainage-contracts.html
Bucharest plans to award a 74
million-lei ($22 million) contract for work to upgrade two
municipal sewage collection systems in the Romanian capital,
 according to a procurement notice published today.   Two additional contracts for about 93 million lei will also
be awarded to drain water from three lakes in Bucharest and to
complete a water treatment plant, according to the European
Union notices.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andra Timu in Bucharest at 
 atimu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
